experiment  data  reliability  was carried out using
the special transitional multiplicity function F2  =
SIG(g,2n)/SIG(g,xn).   In   the  frame  of  the  new
of  partial  reaction  cross  sections the evaluated

cross sections for 158Tb free from the  shortcomings
of experimental neutron multiplicity sorting methods
